name: CRYSTALS & ROSES 12oz travel tumbler
description:
With this unique design you can show off your love of CRYSTALS & ROSES! This 12oz Travel Tumbler comes with a pop-on, straw compatible lid and is dishwasher safe so you can easily clean it. Each tumbler's exterior is hand printed to give a smooth finish and an excellent feel that will not fade, peel or scratch. The interior does not sweat like traditional tumblers, keeping your hands dry. It keeps cold drinks cold and hot drinks hot for hours.

handmade to order in ❤california❤
